{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/TestStore"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:22ComposableArchitecture9TestStoreC12dependencies12Dependencies16DependencyValuesVvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","title":"dependencies","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dependencies","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:12Dependencies16DependencyValuesV","text":"DependencyValues","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"The current dependencies of the test store.","type":"text"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"anchor":"Configuring-a-test-store","generated":true,"title":"Configuring a test store","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/TestStore\/exhaustivity","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/TestStore\/timeout","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/TestStore\/useMainSerialExecutor"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/TestStore\/dependencies"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dependencies","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DependencyValues","preciseIdentifier":"s:12Dependencies16DependencyValuesV"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"set"},{"text":